(8125, 1, '2016-05-06 00:32:57', '2016-05-06 00:32:57', '<img class="alignnone wp-image-8203 size-full" src="http://foxhillfarm.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/image-about.jpg" alt="Katharine &amp; George" width="1000" height="750" />\r\n\r\nBorn in the late-nineteenth century farmhouse on the property, George always hoped he would come back, raise his own family on the farm and work in the family business. Little did he know, his wife would not only embrace farm life, but truly love it and start digging immediately. George and Katharine realized it was a blank slate for growing flowers, grass fed beef, pastured poultry, and most importantly, children! With tons of help from friends and family near and far, Fox Hill Farm is a beautiful place to come plan and celebrate.', 'About', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2016-06-18 13:15:43', '2016-06-18 13:15:43', '', 0, 'http://foxhillfarm.dev/?page_id=8125', 0, 'page', '', 0),
