le leather seating, great lighting and farm treasures used as decor throughout. Clients love these special options for their wedding party. As we only have one wedding per weekend, couples have from Tuesday through Sunday to take their time decorating, preparing and making the celebration their own, then plenty of time to take down the following day. </span></p>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Fox Hill Farm, nestled in the Delaware Valley Highlands, just north of the Poconos and west of the New York border, would love to be your unforgettable and unforgettably beautiful venue!</span></p>', 'Weddings', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8121-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-05 22:43:31', '2016-07-05 22:43:31', '', 8121, 'http://foxhillfarm.dev/2016/07/05/8121-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(8229, 1, '2016-07-05 22:44:38', '2016-07-05 22:44:38', '<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8057" src="http://foxhillfarm.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/blog-01.jpg" alt="blog-01" width="850" height="600" />\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">We are obsessed with flowers at Fox Hill Farm and believe their importance on your wedding day is at the top of the list! As you will see by our extensive</span></p>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">gardens throughout the property, we cannot get enough of flowers. We responsibly grow and use as much from the farm as possible to create a unique </span></p>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">look for your day. Katharine works with couples to create a unique floral look and complete style for weddings not only on the farm, but all over eastern</span></p>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Pennsylvania, New York and beyond.  What we cannot grow, we find; sourcing locally when possible. Experience our obsession with flowers via your wedding!</span></p>', 'Flowers', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8123-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-05 22:44:38', '2016-07-05 22:44:38', '', 8123, 'http://foxhillfarm.dev/2016/07/05/8123-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
