(8343, 1, '2016-07-29 13:51:42', '2016-07-29 13:51:42', '<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8167" src="http://foxhillfarm.dev/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/page-weddings.jpg" alt="page-weddings" width="1000" height="750" />\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">“You’d like to get married here? On the farm?!”</span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<span class="s1">And just like that, barn weddings at Fox Hill Farm began! Three years and many celebrations later, we continue to dedicate ourselves to making each couple’s celebration an elegantly beautiful, memorable and seamless day.</span>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Pond-side outdoor ceremony, cocktail hour in the garden, then dinner and dancing in the 19th century rustic barn make for a fabulous experience throughout the farm on your wedding day here at the farm.  Your creative flair can be added to the treasures found around every corner. These treasures throughout the farm pay homage to the history of farming in northeast Pennsylvania, yet provide a unique atmosphere for you and your guests. The centerpiece of the farm, the barn, still has its original structure. There is a grand entrance, dance floor and  separate catering area, plus a long dining \'hall\' which seats approximately 160 people. Last year saw the completion of our bathhouse adjoining the barn. Both men and women can enjoy the comforts of modern day restrooms, complete with decor people love - even in the bathroom!  Once the lights are on, the tables are set, the music is on, and the party commences, the barn seems to emanate comfort and love. Guests are in awe!</span></p>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Our newly renovated cottage is the perfect place for the bride and her maids to prepare for the big day and it is also available for the newlyweds to stay in while they prepare and/or the night of the wedding. For the groom and groomsmen, also newly renovated and just finished, is the Fox Den! Located in the barn, the den has comfortable leather seating, great lighting and farm treasures used as decor throughout. Clients love these special options for their wedding party. As we only have one wedding per weekend, couples have from Tuesday through Sunday to take their time decorating, preparing and making the celebration their own, then plenty of time to take down the following day. </span></p>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Fox Hill Farm, nestled in the Delaware Valley Highlands, just north of the Poconos and west of the New York border, would love to be your unforgettable and unforgettably beautiful venue!</span></p>\r\n<iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/q6qMv32XvSY" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe>\r\n\r\n<iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RUOf6L29IQo" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe>', 'Weddings', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8121-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-29 13:51:42', '2016-07-29 13:51:42', '', 8121, 'http://foxhillfarm.dev/2016/07/29/8121-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
